snippet.textDisplay: What makes this song is not only the mellifluous vocals but the serene lyrics. They're written in an almost pure form of Hindi which makes one wonder whether this is an old Indian folk song but it's not. Kudos to the writer. The best part of the song is the amazing exuberance of the crew. Everyone looks so damn happy singing this cheerful song. It's a masterpiece in every sense. Zeb has such a wonderful voice. She's lovely and rightly the soul of this song.
